snippet.title: I Tattooed My Eyeballs and Split My Tongue to Look Like a Dragon | This Morning
snippet.description:
Subscribe now for more! http://bit.ly/1JM41yF
23-year-old Amber Luke was tired of feeling 'plain and boring' so nearly £10,000 to transform her look. Amber now has 58 tattoos - including one on her eyes - a split tongue and reshaped ears, but she couldn't be happier with her appearance. 
Broadcast on 26/07/2018
